metadata.description: ArtHouse Spirits DAO is ArtHouse Spirits DAO is the luxury investors club for high-value individuals and like-minded people who share similar luxurious areas of interest. The integral and the central part of DAO is the ArtHouse Spirits Collection which consist of hand-picked barrels and bottles of Dictador rum assemblage, wisely selected by specialists in the field of collectible liquors. This is what brings real, asset-backed value to this NFT collection. Every NFT holder is a partial owner of this Collection.
